[Name] HAL
[Summary] Hardware Abstraction Layer
[License] Academic Free License version 2.1, or the GNU GPL v2
[Description] HAL provides a hardware abstraction layer for desktop \
applications to use to simplify addition of support for new hardware \
and ways to connect that hardware. It provides a list of devices that \
currently exists in its database and can provide information about \
them, if requested.
[Homepage] https://www.freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/hal
